body:
Opt after flatten does not remove unnecessary assigns like below.

```
  assign \inst_m0.ADR_RD  = delay_line1;
  assign \inst_m0.ADR_WR  = delay_line2;
  assign \inst_m0.DATA_IN  = sum_out[3:0];
  assign \inst_m0.RE  = wr_enable;
  assign \inst_m0.WE  = sum_out[0];
  assign \inst_m0.clk  = clk;
```

Please run:

```
read_verilog memory_test.v
hierarchy -top memtest04
proc; opt; flatten; opt; clean
write_verilog -noattr -noexpr fooooo.v
```

[memory_test.v.zip](https://github.com/cliffordwolf/yosys/files/489148/memory_test.v.zip)

